OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry this
OL,6,Fevening with cloud building overnight.
OL,7,FBecoming wet and windy by the Sunday
OL,8,Fmorning with outbreaks of rain moving
OL,9,Fin from the west. Generally a little
OL,10,Fmilder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,13,Fand drizzle, most persistent through
OL,14,Fthe morning with drier interludes
OL,15,Fduring the afternoon. Breezy and
OL,16,Fmilder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
