OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FFurther spells of rain moving in from
OL,7,Fthe west later on Monday with lighter
OL,8,Fwinds. Cloudy on Tuesday with some
OL,9,Fpatchy rain, before turning drier and
OL,10,Fbrighter on Wednesday. Mild.
